## Coding Rules
- TypeScript strict — never use `any`
- App Router patterns only — no Pages Router patterns
- Server Components by default — use `"use client"` only when necessary
- Always use SSH git remote (never HTTPS)
- Env vars: never hardcode secrets — all in Vercel environment variables
- No console.log in production code — use proper error handling
